{
  "stem": "10162.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she was a wonderful woman, by the way.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I loved her, and she loved our whole family.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She was never married.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She always said that she wanted to leave everything to me one day.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And even though we never imagined anything like this to happen, but there was this impending insecurity of some kind of a tragedy in the air because my mother told me to remember Amal-- that was her name-- her address in Vienna because just in case.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You never know where we'll be thrown during-- away from each other.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Maybe that we can always meet there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I still remember her address there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Amalia Begush.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was 26 [NON-ENGLISH] in Vienna.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I never went back there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I never-- well, never even considered it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We stayed in the same apartment, I guess, yes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The one thing about the way I-- we lived-- I think about that sometimes because it is also so different from the way things are in America that I never heard this word 'money' around me.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was just-- you never asked anybody how much money you make, or how do you make a living, or where it comes from.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It just-- I had everything I needed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I never-- I never had more than I needed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It just wasn't-- wasn't something that you would ever want.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was-- wasn't a nice thing to think that way.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we were alone in the apartment.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my grandmother, who lived in Budapest, came down to stay with us because she was afraid of the bombardment in Budapest.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, we had already some bombardments in Debrecen but not such massive than in Budapest.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and I guess the fear was larger in that the capital city would be bombed more.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
